[3
Date: 17 Oct 2001
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: CNN, 17 Oct 2001 [edited
<http://www.cnn.com/2001/HEALTH/conditions/10/17/anthrax/>

Early tests: N.Y. anthrax is same as Fla. strain
------------------------------------------------
Preliminary tests indicate the anthrax found in a letter sent to NBC News
in New York is the same strain of the bacteria as the one identified in
several cases at a Florida tabloid publishing company, sources at the
Centers for Disease Control and Prevention told CNN Wednesday.

