[I have edited out the statements of various politicians who were swept up
in the excitement of the moment. At this time I am more given to accepting
Gen Parker's simple description of the Washington isolates than the others.
This would also match that found in Florida. "Professionally" manufactured
would also cover a pathologically disgruntled academic or professional
microbiologist with access to good institutional facilities. But this powder
is clearly an excellent "flyer."
I apologise to everyone who tried to contact me today who didn't get a
reply. I had a planning meeting this morning on a project here to deal with
our significant infant mortality problem -- 1.1% -- in Baton Rouge, which
approximates to a classroom of kindergarten kids dying each year. It is
largely related to low birth weights. This is more important than the events
in Washington, in my opinion. There were 105 e-mail unread messages awaiting
me at midday. After 30 minutes of dealing with them I had 110 unread
messages. Plus 38 messages on my telephone. - Mod.MHJ
